title: (2014-03) - EastEnders - 17 Episodes
description:
I am not really a fan of EastEnders, but my wife loves it!  I got her the 1985 season and soon realized that there were no other seasonal torrents for the TV show to be found. In fact, it was single episodes only and then, as you went back further, they were harder and harder to download.

So, I managed to scrounge together episodes starting with December 2013 through the current episode dated May 2, 2014.  I will be publishing them in monthly blocks so you don't have to download each episode individually.

This torrent is the complete 15 episodes broadcast in March 2014.

After this, I will upload the month of April and at that point, I'm done.  I do not support torrents that have no audience. These torrents are not being picked up by seeders as well as I had hoped. So I won't waste my time seeding for weeks. I will seed for about 3 or 4 days then wrap it up.

Enjoy.
